3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes a sliding window approach for the algorithm, which involves manipulating data structures. 
4. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper deals with Markov Decision Processes, which can be used to model multi-agent systems.
